[
    {
        "id": "explore_tab",
        "type": "tab",
        "label": "Explore Symbols",
        "disabled": false,
        "info": "S7+ Explore browses the PLC symbol tree and returns flat symbol names in msg.payload (no live values).\n\nRequires the test DBs from plc/s7-1500/ on the PLC with symbolic access enabled.\n\n1) Full catalog browse with msg.meta summary.\n2) Static explore scope: DB_TestSignals configured on the node.\n3) Dynamic scope via msg.exploreScope (DB_Binary or QArea).\n4) Symbol metadata in msg.infos (object and array formats).\n5) Output limit demo (msg.maxSymbols) and Explore → Read pipeline for DB_TestSignals.\n\nSet the PLC IP on the shared S7+ Endpoint config node (PLC) and deploy. Enable debug nodes as needed — full browse payloads can be large."
    },
